-- Shinsei Bank to Advise Takefuji on Selection of Sponsor, Sankei Reports
-- B y   T a k   K u m a k u r a
-- 2010-11-08T22:00:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-08/shinsei-bank-to-advise-takefuji-on-selection-of-sponsor-sankei-reports.html
Shinsei Bank Ltd. agreed to advise
Takefuji Corp. on the selection of its bankruptcy sponsor, the
Sankei newspaper reported, citing the bank. About 20 companies
are seeking to sponsor Takefuji, the report said.   Takefuji, a Japanese consumer lender, filed for bankruptcy
protection in September.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Takehiko Kumakura at 
 tkumakura@bloomberg.net  